    <p>Fire­works will be launched at 10 lo­ca­tions at around 8.20pm af­ter the Pledge Mo­ment, and will last for about five min­utes. The lo­ca­tions are:</p>
    <p>• Ang Mo Kio</p>
    <p>• Bis­han</p>
    <p>• Buona Vista</p>
    <p>• Jurong Lake Gar­dens*</p>
    <p>• Ma­rina Reser­voir*</p>
    <p>• Pung­gol</p>
    <p>• Sem­bawang</p>
    <p>• Tampines</p>
    <p>• Wood­lands</p>
    <p>• Yew Tee</p>
    <p>(* venues will be closed to the pub­lic)</p>
    <p>Po­lice re­mind those who want to view the ac­tiv­i­ties in pub­lic spa­ces to wear masks, re­main in groups of five or fewer, and main­tain 1m safe dis­tanc­ing.</p>


